prompt_template:
Task: For each Hypothesis (H1...Hk, up to 10), decide which response (1 or 2) better aligns with it given the User Prompt; if neither applies or alignment is equal/unclear even after tie-breakers, answer "N/A". Output JSON only.

**Hypotheses:**
{hypotheses}

**User Prompt:**
{prompt}

**Model 1 Response:**
{response1}

**Model 2 Response:**
{response2}

Return exactly one JSON object mapping each provided hypothesis label to a decision. Every given hypothesis must have exactly one decision:
{{"H1": <1|2|"N/A">, "H2": <1|2|"N/A">, ...}}
